[
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶雲經卷第六",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "梁扶南三藏曼陀羅仙譯",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！菩薩復有十法名為信敬。何等為",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善根深厚宿殖德本、得於正見不隨他信不歸依他、志性恒正不為虛妄、其心質直無有諂曲、利根智慧功德具足、除諸陰蓋其心清淨、常依善知識遠離惡知識、摧伏憍慢、聞深妙法能善諦受、終不顛倒妄解如來甚深法藏威德自在。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具此十事是名菩薩能多信敬。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今於如來大威德所願說少法，令我得聞。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝今善聽，當為說之，如來要法、威德少分。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」「善哉，世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願為演說。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如來大慈等與一切眾生樂，若於一眾生起慈心時，乃至十方眾生亦復如是，遍一切眾生界亦滿虛空界，無能遍知如來甚深境界邊際。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c28_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如來有大悲心，不與聲聞、辟支佛共。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0234c29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來於一眾生起於悲心，乃至一切眾生亦復如是，為作利益。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來大悲無有邊際，非諸二乘所能究竟。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a02_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來說法不可窮盡，能於一時普為十方眾生說法，若一劫、百千萬億劫、無量阿僧祇劫作如是說，一切眾生無有能知如來說法邊際本末。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「假使無量眾生一時問難，而如來於一念中各隨其類一音能答，然如來辯才無有窮盡。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如來有無量阿僧祇禪定三昧之所行處。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使一切眾生皆得十住，各各皆入無量三昧，於百千劫中各入異定，如是經無量劫猶不能盡知如來三昧境界。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a11_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如來又作無量阿僧祇應身，令一切眾生應受化者，悉見如來皆現其前，於一念頃，一一色相皆生信解，各有差別。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來又復一時皆現其前，隨其所應而為說法，令諸眾生悉皆受行。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來天眼所見境界無量無邊，非肉眼所見。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是天眼境界，如來於一念中悉皆見之，如觀掌中阿摩勒果。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如來天耳所聞境界無量無邊，如上天眼，一切眾生、異類音聲，隨其大小於一念頃悉分別知。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如來復有無量無邊無礙智慧，無與等者、不可為譬。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a21_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切眾生若心念所知，隨其根性種種差別，如來於一剎那頃悉分別知。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "隨彼眾生各各所念、各各所作、隨造善惡所得業報，如來能以三達無礙智慧，於剎那頃悉分別知。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a25_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來常在禪定。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來終無忘念。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a26_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來諸根無有錯謬，如來斷一切結使，其心寂靜；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若雜結使，其心散亂，離清淨法。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235a28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來已離一切業習，塵垢永盡，無漏、無為，於法自在，一切三昧三摩提無量境界，已度彼岸。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b01_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如來常在三昧、常一威儀，乃至涅槃。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如來於無量百千億劫修集所得，無有眾生能思惟分別知其量者。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來不從阿僧祇劫積集功德耶？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不爾。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b05_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b05_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩不能思議如來境界。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來境界不可思量，但為淺近眾生，說三阿僧祇修集所得，菩薩而實發心以來不可計數。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若眾生久修善根、植諸業行、除去蓋障、多有信解、近於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提、得聞如來無量威德，聞是法已歡喜信樂，況復受持、讀誦、書寫、供養、為人廣說？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是之人不久亦當得大威德，堪任法器。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如汝所說，如是如是。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如此眾生為佛所護，久種善根、親近諸佛，聞佛有大威德，善男子、善女人而於其中不生疑惑。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子、善女人心不錯亂，不錯亂故，思惟如來有大威德，深生殷重信樂之心，七日七夜著鮮淨衣恭敬供養，專念如來大功德寶，心不移易必得見佛；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不滿七日，乃至一日一夜，命終之時亦得見佛。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "頗有眾生於如來所說不信受者？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛即答言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有眾生聞佛所說不肯信受，深生惱害，於說法者生惡知識想，以是因緣，身壞命終墮於地獄。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b24_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若聞如來有大威德，生世尊想、生大師想，如此之人已於前世得聞如來無量功德，以是因緣今復續聞。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即自思惟：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我等先身必曾從佛聞如此法。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235b28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」爾時，如來即出廣長舌相自覆其面，其舌廣長踰於髮際乃至覆頭，覆頭已復覆其身，覆身已覆師子座，又覆菩薩、聲聞、緣覺、護世四天王、梵天、帝釋，遍覆一切無量大眾。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛還攝舌相告諸大眾：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子等！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c03_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是舌相無虛妄耶。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若信是事，長夜安隱，得諸利樂。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」說是語時，八萬四千眾生得無生法忍，無量眾生遠塵離垢得法眼淨，無量眾生未發菩提心者皆發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛復告除蓋障菩薩言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩復有十法名滿世間善。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c10_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖說於色，而於實諦不見有相，亦不著色相；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c11_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受、想、行、識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖說於地，而於實諦不見有相，亦不著地相；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "水、火、風、空識亦復如是。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖說於眼，而於實諦不見有相，亦不著眼相；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c14_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖說鼻、舌、身、意法，而於實諦不見有相，亦不著意法等相。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖說有我，而於實諦不見有相，亦不著我相；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眾生壽者、命者、丈夫人，而於實諦不見有相，亦不取著。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但世諦假施設有，第一義諦則不可得，亦不取著；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世諦假施設有，第一義諦無有體相，亦不取著。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世流布中而有佛法差別，若於實諦亦無佛法善惡之相；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但世諦中而有菩提，第一義諦則無菩提，亦無取著。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假施設法名為世諦，終不說世諦為第一義諦。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c23_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩善於世諦，不名為善於第一義諦。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具此十事是名菩薩滿世間善。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩復有十法名為善說第一義諦。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "成就無生法忍、成就滅法、成就不壞法、非造作法、是究竟法、非處所法、無言語法、無調戲法、是寂滅法、是賢聖法。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0235c29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第一義諦不生、不滅，非壞、非所作，亦非盡，非文字，亦非調戲所得。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a02_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第一義諦非言語道，法相寂滅，賢聖之所證覺。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a03_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "第一義諦非壞敗相，諸佛出世及不出世，法相常爾。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是因緣故，菩薩剃除鬚髮、信家非家、出家學道、正信出家、身服袈裟、著壞色衣，精勤修道如救頭然，捨諸虛妄，志求實法。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無實法則虛出家，諸佛如來亦虛出世。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是因緣，有真實法。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a09_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具此十事是名菩薩善解第一義諦。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩復有十法名為善知十二因緣。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善知體相空、善知剎那法、善知不堅法、善知如影、如水中月、如呼聲響、善知法如幻、善知法如電、善知法如焰、如因緣生法。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a14_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此悉是空，一剎那頃不堅法，如是，乃至因緣生法，此法生亦見生、住亦見住、異壞亦見異壞。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩如是思惟：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『以何因緣生？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以何因緣滅？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』菩薩復更思惟：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a18_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『因無明故，能生諸法；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a18_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無明力故，諸法得出。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切諸法，無明為導；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切諸法，依止無明。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依無明故，能生於行；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依行故，生識；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識因緣生名色、名色因緣生六入、六入因緣生觸、觸因緣生受；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受因緣故，凡愚眾生於受少分便起染愛；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愛因緣生取、取因緣生有、有因緣生生、生因緣有老死；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "丈夫人老死，死因緣憂、悲、苦、惱眾苦聚集，以是因緣生大苦陰。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』以深智慧慇懃方便，當斷無明、拔無明根，滅於無明，無明相應法一切盡滅。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如命根盡時，諸根都盡；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無明盡時，依無明法一切悉盡。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無明滅故，諸煩惱滅；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236a29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "煩惱滅故，生死因皆滅；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生死滅故，近於涅槃。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具此十事是名菩薩善知十二因緣。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩復有十法名善知我。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b03_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩作如是觀察：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我生誰家？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為是婆羅門家？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b04_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為是剎利家？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為是長者家？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為是下賤家？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b05_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』菩薩雖生上族家而無憍慢想。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若生下賤處而作是念：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我本曾作不善諸業，以惡業故，今生下賤家。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』以是因緣多修厭惡，多修厭惡故欲得出家。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「既出家已作是思惟：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我為何事而求出家？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫出家法為自度脫亦度於彼，以是因緣，不應懈怠而自懶墮。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「作是思惟：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我今出家當何不善？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有少惡速疾除斷，於諸善法深起愛樂、歡喜無厭，所未斷惡方便令斷。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』如是復更觀察：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我等出家，云何增廣善法？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善法增已，當倍愛樂、深心歡喜；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善法未增當令增廣。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b15_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今依怙師僧增廣善法，以是因緣於和上所——若持戒、若破戒，若多聞、若少聞，若聰明、若無智——悉皆恭敬生世尊想。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於諸世尊恭敬供養，信樂歡喜；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於和上所亦復如是，於阿闍梨復生恭敬。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我依阿闍梨故，善法增廣，菩提法分未滿足者當令使滿、諸結未斷者當令使斷。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b22_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』於阿闍梨復生和上想，供養如前，愛樂歡喜，增長右法、損減左法。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，左法不令增長。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復更觀察：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『誰是我世尊？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切種智是我世尊；",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能一切覺、能一切說、救濟世間、憐愍眾生、具大悲心、是大福田，是我世尊、天人之師。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』以是因緣、以是相貌，應生信敬，愛樂歡喜。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b27_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「又復思惟：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我得大利，遇佛、世尊、如來制戒，我今寧捨身命終不毀犯如來制戒。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236b29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是名善受佛教。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「『我今當應從誰受供？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如我今者，當從剎利、婆羅門、聚落、城邑受彼供施，令彼果報尊貴富樂。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我亦不應虛受人供，如是剎利、婆羅門、聚落、城邑皆作何想？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今思惟有何功德而施飲食？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "剎利、婆羅門、聚落、城邑當念我是沙門、作福田想，我今應當具滿沙門所行之道、比丘功德、沙門功德，福田淨業宜稱其名。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c07_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「『我今處生死中當自拔出，我今已得出家善利、我今初得無上大利、我得出家即是無上大利、我今能稱出家之法亦是無上大利，我今當勤精進，遠離懈怠，亦疾速出生死災患。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩出家常應執念如是思惟。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具此十事是名菩薩善知於我。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c13_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩復有十法名善知世法。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於自高人起卑賤想、於憍慢人起恭敬想、於諂曲人起質直想、於妄語人起真實想、於憎惡人起愛樂想、於剛強人起柔軟想、於不忍人起忍辱想、於瞋忿人起慈心想、於苦惱人起悲心想、於多貪人起施與想。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具此十事是名菩薩善知世法。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩復有十法名能生淨佛國土。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "持戒清淨無闕戒無嫌戒、於一切眾生心常平等、同其事業具諸功德、遠離名聞讚歎利養、不染八法深信不疑、勤修精進無有懈怠、攝心禪定無諸錯亂、善修多聞遠離無智、利根聰慧滅除愚闇、於瞋惱眾生恒修慈心。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」除蓋障菩薩白佛言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若十事不具，能生淨土不？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛即答言：",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c27_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能於一事具足無闕，當知十事悉皆清淨，以是義故，名具十事得生淨土。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0236c29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具此十事是名菩薩能生淨佛國土。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩復有十法名胎不染污。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "作諸形像、如來塔寺若有毀壞嚴飾修治、復以諸香泥塗於佛塔如來形像、常以香湯洗浴、於如來塔塗掃清淨、於父母所躬自供養、於和上阿闍梨同梵行者心常恭敬供養不為財利、以此善根迴與一切眾生、願令皆得胎不染污、心常殷重如是思惟。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a08_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具此十事是名菩薩胎不染污。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a09_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩復有十法，名捨家出家。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為十？",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a10_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無所受用、於可染處終不親近、背於五欲、除諸愛渴、於如來所制禁戒終不毀犯、少欲知足、衣服飲食床敷臥具趣得支命終不貪積、於五欲所常生畏怖、恒念厭離、修集善法。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "具此十事是名菩薩捨家出家。",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a15_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶雲經卷第六",
        "from": "T16n0658_006:0237a16_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]